systemFeature.name: N
systemFeature.description: Average number of customers in the steady state system

systemFeature.name: Q
systemFeature.description: Average number of customers in the queue (not including thosein service)

systemFeature.name: T
systemFeature.description: The mean total time (both service and queing time) a customer spends in the system

systemFeature.name: W
systemFeature.description: Average time in the queue

systemFeature.name: D<sup>2</sup>(N)
systemFeature.description: Variance of N

systemFeature.name: D<sup>2</sup>(Q)
systemFeature.description: Variance of Q

systemFeature.name: D<sup>2</sup>(T)
systemFeature.description: Variance of T

systemFeature.name: D<sup>2</sup>(W)
systemFeature.description: Variance of W

systemFeature.name: D<sup>2</sup>[Q|Q>0]
systemFeature.description: Variance of queue length of nonempty queues in steady state

systemFeature.name: E[Q|Q>0]
systemFeature.description: Average queue length of nonempty queues when the system is in steady state

systemFeature.name: F<sub>T</sub>(t)
systemFeature.description: Distribution function for mean total time a customer spends in the system

systemFeature.name: F<sub>W</sub>(t)
systemFeature.description: Distribution function for time in the queue

systemFeature.name: P<sub>n</sub>
systemFeature.description: Steady state probability that there are n customers in the system

systemFeature.name: P[N>=n]
systemFeature.description: P[N>=n]

systemFeature.name: P[T>t]
systemFeature.description: The probability that the mean total time a customer spends in the system is greater then t

systemFeature.name: P[W>t]
systemFeature.description: The probability that the time in the queue is greater then t

systemFeature.name: π<sub>T[90]</sub>
systemFeature.description: Symbol for 90-th percentile waiting time in the system

systemFeature.name: π<sub>T[95]</sub>
systemFeature.description: Symbol for 95-th percentile waiting time in the system

systemFeature.name: π<sub>T[r]</sub>
systemFeature.description: Symbol for r-th percentile waiting time in the system

systemFeature.name: π<sub>W[90]</sub>
systemFeature.description: Symbol for 90-th percentile queuing time

systemFeature.name: π<sub>W[95]</sub>
systemFeature.description: Symbol for 95-th percentile queuing time

systemFeature.name: π<sub>W[r]</sub>
systemFeature.description: Symbol for r-th percentile queuing time

systemFeature.name: ρ
systemFeature.description: Traffic intensity, unit of measure is the erlang
